Good Evening.
After searching my mind for a while trying to think of something to draw, I decided to take a break. I lit some candles, fixed a margarita and started listening to music. After a few songs, I received some inspiration! 
I hope you like it

www.creativebrushwork.com

Hello!
After a long hiatus, I have returned to the Art World. My story is an interesting one and my artwork is interesting also. I intend to share both through this journal and my website: 

http://www.creativebrushwork.com/

I hope you enjoy my journal and will post often!

Airizona
